###########################################Problem Statement###############################################
there are two files. One file contains employee information.
emp_id, emp_name
second file contains employee transactions.
emp_id, trans_id, trans_amount

second file is huge and can not be loaded in memory at one go.
print employee name and total transaction amount as follows:
Emp_name, Total_Transaction
Shashank, 10000
Mahesh, 20000

